title: Jungle Girl (1941) Old Time Serial (OTS)
description:
Here we are again...  It's 1941 and Jungle Girl is defending the natives again.  In, what else, glorious Black and White.  Seems appropriate...

Plot:  Dr. John Meredith has been driven from civilization by the criminal
       activities of his twin brother.  With his infant daughter, he settles
       in the African jungle, where his ability to cure the native ills has
       resulted in his virtual control of the Masamba tribes, who possess
       vast diamond mines coveted by a gang of crooks
